  <brief_title>Placental Cord Drainage Versus no Placental Drainage in the Management of Third Stage of Labour</brief_title>
  <acronym>PLCD</acronym>
  <official_title>Placental Cord Drainage Versus no Placental Drainage in the Management of Third Stage of Labour: Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
